{"tid":1476650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲想醜化失明女士","createTime":"2019-08-16T01:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T07:44:15.000Z","uid":47647,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6c7fc64b3964dfbbe85c5f4b9e2577848ee33970","tid":1476650,"uid":47647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2Zm7A9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2Zm7A9.png&h=a9aea264&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc60fff26d71c10a4548e03b7b4e1421cb58cec1","tid":1476650,"uid":79046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:28:27.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行過路過入嚟望下，千載難逢嘅大好機會！！十八區we connect，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">823人鏈823人鏈823人鏈</span></span></strong>，百萬人齊築香江路！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［和理非升級］一生人一次嘅機會嚟喇！！！！想唔想上Buzzfeed 9GAG？！？！？！？！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475842\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475842</a>"},{"pid":"ece3b3fe80c99771bd4812f25d0050aba583eeca","tid":1476650,"uid":101623,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:29:09.000Z","msg":"借個位！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我想講，<br />\n當大家煲緊<br />\n一818要和理非既時候，<br />\n呢兩日就分別爆岀左兩單野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一單</strong><br />\n係聲稱有人（男女都有）係警署<br />\n俾人全祼搜身，盡情羞辱。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>第二單就係，</strong><br />\n話有狗係skout到爆<br />\n話爆眼女仔係臥底做<br />\n又話三個警察拉女人房慢慢玩<br />\n<br />\n但兩單野都好明顯無根無據<br />\n第一單就咁話已fc就當自己真係fc左<br />\n第二單更加係錯漏百岀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好果爆眼女仔係臥底整傷<br />\n咁點會係用布袋彈？？？？</span><br />\n（似唔似有造謠者<br />\n自己都信左藍絲既鋼珠爆眼論！）<br />\n<br />\n而正常釣過9公既人都知！<br />\n釣9公係要好有耐性<br />\n唔會問一問就自己爆晒岀<br />\n中間所有料都基乎無相隔其他寒暄<br />\n真確性非常之受質疑！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我極度懷疑！</span><br />\n有人想係呢個星期<br />\n散布不實又令髮指既指控<br />\n<strong>想煽動大家係818衝爆佢！<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n大家一定要保持冷靜！<br />\n唔好俾仇恨掩蓋自己既理智同判斷！<br />\n我絕對唔係話啲狗做唔岀呢啲行為！<br />\n<br />\n但如果一句fc就信<br />\n一句skout自爆就信<br />\n<br />\n<strong>咁同藍絲信街坊話冇放催淚彈<br />\n信鋼珠爆眼<br />\n信掹槍警俾人踢爆膀胱有乜分別！？</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>保持理智啊手足！</strong>"},{"pid":"2b734e1580d2184283b735b5c6f254bcb0491f6c","tid":1476650,"uid":105976,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:29:48.000Z","msg":"呢D野就唔好上黎啦<br />\n睇都費事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4d7bd4c0aa7f38ba82208bf0de9474a6605bd2","tid":1476650,"uid":33645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e9b4fca9b7150f29204d1fedb9ca239ae6c437","tid":1476650,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:31:46.000Z","msg":"所以話我地係做假呢方面真係唔夠人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍屍個智商本身就已經唔高"},{"pid":"6b7e01681e548b4312f8c6da29c1258a49d56fde","tid":1476650,"uid":8086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:33:36.000Z","msg":"會信個啲都傻西黎"},{"pid":"72670eff7359780c29ec3e58449d4317485478bb","tid":1476650,"uid":19062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全亞洲數一數二法治之都竟然係乜都黑<br />\n班友仲會住係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832cccb149ecfe2aa37a404e113500d990988981","tid":1476650,"uid":276162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0WQd7h.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://